{"1":[[1121,1201,"What do you want?"],[1234,1459,"To teach little miss perfect a lesson."],[1760,1835,"Get her!"],[1926,1960,"No."],[2043,2085,"No, what are you-"],[2085,2223,"Get her up against the wall."],[2335,2410,"Let go of me!"],[3820,3891,"Sir,"],[3941,4012,"we found her,"],[4074,4200,"your long-lost granddaughter."],[4333,4412,"Where is she?"],[4446,4571,"Juvenile Detention Center."],[4583,4704,"Serving time for a crime"],[4704,4813,"she did not commit."],[5042,5192,"She is the last"],[5217,5409,"of the Lancaster bloodline."],[5434,5572,"Get her out of there"],[5651,5784,"before something happens to her,"],[5784,5843,"Stirling."],[5876,6006,"Sir, we will find the heiress"],[6006,6135,"and bring her back safe and sound."],[6135,6218,"You can count on it."],[6322,6452,"Don't let me down, Stirling."],[6898,6965,"Oh,"],[6965,7057,"do you think your little boyfriend"],[7057,7152,"is gonna save you?"],[7244,7340,"Get her on the ground."],[7545,7686,"I'm getting tortured in Juvie"],[7686,7828,"all because I took the fall"],[7828,8020,"for my quarterback boyfriend."],[8466,8608,"What are you gonna do with that?"],[8662,8758,"Get her hair."],[8817,8913,"Not my hair, no!"],[8917,9046,"Stay the fuck down!"],[9171,9280,"Stop it! No!"],[9321,9430,"No!"],[9613,9722,"No, no, no."],[9722,9851,"No, what are you doing?"],[10164,10226,"What the fuck-"],[10226,10306,"Hold her still!"],[10397,10485,"Hold still."],[10502,10627,"Your face is next."],[10835,10894,"No, no, no."],[10902,11040,"Get your hands off of her!"],[11373,11436,"Get up!"],[11569,11632,"Give me that."],[11657,11778,"You, get up against the wall!"],[11891,12003,"We finally found you."],[12066,12145,"The long lost"],[12145,12253,"Lancaster heiress."]],"2":[[104,241,"How did the richest heiress"],[241,412,"in the country end up in juvie?"],[475,725,"How dare you attack her?"],[784,892,"Do you have a death wish?"],[1005,1088,"Get them out of here!"],[1109,1234,"Let the warden deal with them."],[1559,1668,"Miss Lancaster."],[3545,3636,"What the hell?"],[3862,3953,"You can't just walk out of here"],[3953,4004,"with an inmate."],[4033,4070,"Shut up!"],[4175,4229,"You know who you're"],[4229,4316,"talking about?"],[4412,4596,"That's the Lancaster guard."],[4596,4754,"They serve and protect"],[4754,4875,"the members of the richest"],[4892,5034,"and most powerful family"],[5034,5180,"in this country."],[5342,5497,"Say goodbye, ladies."],[5593,5676,"Toodles."],[5684,5860,"You won't be tasting that kind of freedom"],[5860,6006,"for a long time."],[6139,6193,"Let's go."],[6193,6306,"Put them in the cage!"],[7273,7432,"My boyfriend will be so happy"],[7432,7536,"I got released early."],[7607,7711,"I have to call him."],[8808,8942,"Hey, you've reached Jake."],[8942,9046,"I'm not available right now,"],[9046,9150,"but leave me a message."],[9217,9305,"Jake, there's no way"],[9305,9409,"Sierra will show her face"],[9409,9517,"this semester, right?"],[9605,9693,"No, she's locked up until"],[9693,9763,"graduation, babe."]],"3":[[0,129,"Hey, you've reached Jake."],[129,233,"I'm not available right now,"],[233,337,"but leave me a message."],[588,717,"Excuse me, mister..."],[767,913,"You can call me Stirling."],[1046,1142,"Stirling."],[1142,1343,"Are you sure that I'm an heiress?"],[1418,1484,"I thought"],[1484,1580,"my birth family"],[1580,1735,"wanted nothing to do with me."],[1747,1881,"Your grandfather's been searching"],[1881,2047,"for you for 12 years."],[2060,2214,"He'd recognize that moon"],[2214,2318,"birthmark anywhere."],[2569,2656,"He's on his way back to the"],[2656,2752,"States now."],[2752,2877,"He's donated millions"],[2877,2998,"to the Hawthorne Prep School"],[3040,3215,"to ensure that you wouldn't endure"],[3215,3374,"that kind of abuse ever again."],[3470,3549,"You'll go back there"],[3549,3628,"again tomorrow."],[3645,3807,"I'm going back to Hawthorne?"],[3870,4016,"I'm gonna see Jake again."],[4379,4471,"We're gonna join homecoming"],[4471,4562,"court next year."],[4571,4646,"I promise."],[4729,4804,"I can't wait to make you"],[4804,4867,"my queen."],[4934,5025,"Jake."],[5588,5697,"Hey, you've reached Jake."],[5697,5801,"I'm not available right now,"],[5801,5851,"but leave me a message-"],[5851,5980,"Why isn't he answering?"],[6385,6493,"Just stop the car."],[6510,6606,"Can we go to Hawthorne now?"],[6760,6856,"Wait, wait, wait."],[6856,6948,"Take this."],[6948,7007,"Ok?"],[7182,7286,"And,"],[7399,7524,"your mother’s bracelet."],[7553,7657,"Your grandfather wanted you"],[7657,7716,"to have that."],[7766,7978,"It's a Lancaster heirloom."],[8821,8863,"And look,"],[8863,8954,"you need anything,"],[8954,9063,"you call me, ok?"],[9104,9154,"Ok."],[9192,9330,"All right. Let her out."],[10135,10301,"Do you still love me, Jake?"],[10944,11086,"Bro, we need to find you a date"],[11086,11223,"for the homecoming dance next week."],[11244,11340,"You're the school's new star"],[11340,11436,"quarterback."],[11436,11582,"You need a fine queen"],[11582,11640,"by your side."],[11665,11753,"Yah, bro, but,"],[11770,11845,"I'm tired of these stuck-up"],[11845,11932,"rich girls, man."],[12057,12183,"Bro, I want to find her."],[13355,13392,"It's..."],[13626,13680,"you."]],"4":[[221,291,"It's..."],[496,563,"you."],[809,963,"The girl that saved me that day."],[1130,1288,"Guys, we can talk about this."],[1288,1368,"Guys. Come on."],[1368,1480,"Guys, please. Please."],[1480,1593,"Help me! Help me!"],[1593,1668,"Help me!"],[1705,1801,"Hug me. Quickly."],[1810,1906,"They can't see you."],[1931,2102,"Where'd he go? Where'd he go?"],[2102,2210,"He went that way!"],[2227,2289,"Get him!"],[2298,2339,"Move!"],[2506,2560,"He's over here."],[2560,2702,"Now. Go quickly, before"],[2702,2761,"they see you."],[2773,2852,"Thank you."],[3449,3507,"Tell me your name."],[4045,4112,"Jake!"],[4279,4350,"Jake."],[6385,6468,"Jake."],[6493,6556,"Jake."],[6644,6756,"Where is he going?"],[6769,6831,"Jake."],[6940,7032,"Excuse me. Sorry."],[7040,7077,"Jake."],[7136,7211,"Bestie!"],[7290,7374,"Oh my God!"],[7374,7511,"What are you doing here?"],[7511,7711,"I can't let Jake see this slimy bitch."],[7724,7857,"He's mine now."],[7857,7945,"Fallon. Thank god."],[7945,8053,"Have you seen Jake?"],[8074,8137,"Well, you better"],[8137,8254,"give me a hug first, girlie."],[8591,8700,"Go back to juvie,"],[8700,8854,"you sad little stray."],[10010,10085,"Thank you."],[10139,10218,"Grayson."],[10289,10385,"Now we're even."],[10585,10689,"Hey, son."],[10689,10806,"The missing Lancaster heiress"],[10806,10919,"has been found!"],[10919,11140,"And she's enrolling in Hawthorne today."],[11140,11294,"Now, her father and I"],[11294,11369,"were dear friends."],[11369,11536,"So, I need you to look out for her."],[11536,11665,"I will."],[11957,12045,"Wait, wait."],[12278,12429,"The Lancaster crest."],[12449,12608,"Could the girl who saved me be..."],[12654,12762,"the heiress?"]],"5":[[58,179,"But she seems so..."],[462,521,"different."],[642,738,"What's your name?"],[796,875,"Sierra L-"],[875,959,"I'm here with"],[959,1109,"Hawthorne Morning Report,"],[1146,1284,"and today, we're announcing"],[1284,1409,"homecoming queen."],[1914,2143,"I have to find my boyfriend."],[2181,2248,"Ok, cool."],[2293,2406,"Now you've got my number."],[2556,2660,"In case you need anything."],[2731,2790,"Wait, hey."],[3094,3219,"Take my lucky gold coin."],[3586,3699,"Helped me get the state championship"],[3699,3799,"win in my last school."],[3941,3991,"Think you might need it"],[3991,4112,"a little more than I do."],[5930,6010,"They're about to announce"],[6010,6135,"homecoming King and Queen."],[6168,6343,"Aren't you so excited, Jakey?"],[6619,6706,"You better not be thinking"],[6706,6794,"about that delinquent"],[6794,6886,"ex of yours."],[6919,6977,"Nah."],[7073,7140,"Because of you,"],[7228,7323,"I'm second string quarterback"],[7323,7403,"on the football team,"],[7432,7486,"and"],[7486,7574,"I have a summer internship"],[7574,7665,"with your dad's company."],[7766,7836,"You're a baddie."],[7899,8008,"Sierra's just a poor nobody."],[8220,8279,"Oh!"],[8591,8675,"Oh my God."],[8746,8792,"Oh my God!"],[8792,8896,"The rumors are true."],[8971,9175,"They just announced that"],[9175,9338,"they found the Lancaster heiress."],[9338,9559,"She enrolled here today."],[9588,9647,"Yeah!"],[9647,9713,"Isn't she like,"],[9713,9843,"the richest girl in the country?"],[9868,9959,"Her grandpa funds"],[9959,10030,"this whole school."],[10064,10147,"Once I become besties"],[10147,10210,"with the heiress,"],[10210,10410,"I'll make sure you're top of the class"],[10414,10539,"and maybe even get you a spot"],[10539,10602,"at Harvard,"],[10635,10764,"if you behave."],[10814,10923,"God, I'm so glad"],[10923,11006,"I dumped Sierra for you."],[11165,11294,"And here are your nominees for"],[11294,11490,"homecoming court."],[11519,11703,"First up is Jake Walker."],[12645,12983,"And his queen, Fallon Blakely."]],"6":[[12,308,"This is my queen right here."],[312,517,"He called me his queen, too."],[517,684,"He said he loved me."],[684,779,"Without this hot piece helping"],[779,867,"me study,"],[867,1042,"I would never have aced my final exam"],[1042,1163,"last year."],[1163,1343,"I owe her everything."],[1343,1497,"And I love her."],[1497,1797,"And she is fine as hell!"],[2298,2598,"He has no idea who he just betrayed."],[2823,2948,"We interrupt our programming to"],[2948,3115,"announce that the Lancaster heiress"],[3115,3207,"is here."],[3207,3461,"She has just arrived on campus."],[3766,3924,"I heard her grandpa owns like,"],[3924,4020,"six private islands."],[4020,4179,"Wait! Shit, that's insane!"],[4179,4383,"I bet she throws the sickest parties."],[4550,4650,"If we get her to endorse"],[4650,4775,"us, there's no way we won't win"],[4775,4946,"homecoming king and queen."],[4959,5113,"Don't embarrass me."],[5226,5376,"Welcome to Hawthorne Prep."],[5626,5689,"No way."],[5880,5905,"It's you."]],"7":[[150,321,"What?"],[321,450,"I thought you'd be excited"],[450,621,"to see me."],[621,800,"That's Jake's ex."],[800,834,"I heard"],[834,988,"she went to that juvie shithole,"],[988,1101,"Saint Mary's."],[1138,1376,"My God, she looks pissed."],[1376,1568,"Is she gonna pull a knife?"],[1614,1785,"Who let that bitch back in?"],[1785,1926,"Reform school rejects"],[1926,2081,"should be banned from"],[2081,2227,"walking these halls."],[2435,2531,"Get her out of here."],[2531,2619,"The heiress is coming and"],[2619,2769,"I can't be seen with this"],[2769,2919,"dirty criminal."],[3011,3128,"Sierra, what are you doing here?"],[3128,3290,"What the hell are you doing"],[3290,3424,"running for homecoming court"],[3424,3616,"with my ex best friend."],[3616,3728,"You said that we would run"],[3728,3858,"together senior year."],[3858,3978,"Do you seriously think"],[3978,4129,"I still want that?"],[4129,4404,"I upgraded, Sierra."],[4404,4475,"Why would I settle for"],[4475,4558,"Saint Mary's trash"],[4558,4658,"when I can have a hot,"],[4658,4867,"rich cheerleader like Fallon?"],[4867,5055,"She can get me the top of my class"],[5055,5192,"and get me into Harvard."],[5192,5359,"Well, then I hope you like botched"],[5359,5538,"spray tans and daddy issue."],[5584,5689,"Bitch!"],[5764,5943,"Sierra, you're broke as hell."],[5943,6056,"Okay, you look straight"],[6056,6106,"ran through and"],[6106,6185,"you're not even smart."],[6235,6468,"You don't deserve to be with me."],[6944,7065,"I don't know how you scammed your"],[7065,7186,"way back into Hawthorne,"],[7186,7328,"but you won't last."],[7328,7478,"You'll be sent back to prison school"],[7478,7545,"and I'll never have to see"],[7545,7757,"your busted ass face again."],[7757,7962,"They think they can tear me down."],[7962,8141,"But I'm not here for their approval."],[8141,8266,"I'm here to take what"],[8266,8441,"they think I can't have."],[8529,8771,"I aced that final exam."],[8771,8921,"You failed and I took the fall for you."],[8921,9063,"You wouldn't be here"],[9063,9200,"if it weren't for me."],[9338,9480,"And you want to know how I"],[9480,9747,"scammed my way back here?"],[9747,10018,"My grandfather owns this school"],[10018,10181,"and he donates millions to"],[10181,10314,"Ivy League universities."],[10314,10477,"So you want to be at the"],[10477,10602,"top of the senior class?"],[10706,11006,"You want a spot at Harvard?"],[11048,11127,"Well, then you better"],[11127,11265,"get on your knees"],[11265,11428,"and beg for it."]],"8":[[0,300,"You want a spot at Harvard?"],[342,412,"Well, then you better"],[412,721,"get on your knees and beg for it."],[1130,1343,"Yeah right."],[1343,1472,"The Lancaster heiress'"],[1472,1685,"family owns Hawthorne."],[1685,1764,"Your grandpa is probably"],[1764,1856,"drinking himself to death"],[1856,1985,"in some trailer park."],[2097,2264,"You should leave, Sierra."],[2264,2389,"Your lies are getting sad."],[2389,2510,"I spent a year"],[2510,2727,"getting tortured at Saint Mary's."],[2727,2861,"If anyone is leaving,"],[2861,2957,"it's you."],[2957,3144,"Oh, we all knew"],[3144,3286,"you were bound for Saint Mary's."],[3286,3586,"I mean, look at you."],[3682,3766,"Yeah, what the hell"],[3766,3962,"happened to her hair?"],[3962,4058,"Oh, dude,"],[4058,4104,"she looks like"],[4104,4154,"she got caught"],[4154,4325,"in the fucking lawnmower."],[4425,4542,"No. Guys, guys."],[4542,4821,"It's sad, honestly."],[4821,4954,"She obviously can't afford"],[4954,5276,"new clothes or a new outfit or..."],[5359,5551,"a haircut."],[5851,6122,"Oh, I bet she was giving blowjobs"],[6122,6306,"to juvie boys for lunch money."],[6439,6523,"That's what desperate"],[6523,6602,"bitches do."],[6752,6969,"If it's money you need,"],[6994,7094,"I've got plenty."],[7132,7211,"You're gonna have to"],[7211,7294,"work for it though."],[7478,7640,"Virgil, the Virgin,"],[7640,7782,"come here."],[7782,7845,"Yeah."],[8103,8404,"Come here. - Oh shit!"],[8837,8942,"It's Kevin."],[8942,9167,"Okay, Kevin."],[9167,9234,"Kevin,"],[9234,9534,"the virgin needs some love."],[9534,9622,"Get down."],[9943,10051,"Why don't you show him"],[10051,10105,"how you did it"],[10105,10247,"the old Saint Mary's way."],[10247,10310,"Yeah."],[10798,10969,"Come on, Sierra, there's more"],[10969,11115,"where that came from."],[12045,12191,"I don't need your money."],[12191,12370,"My family's got millions."]],"9":[[191,325,"Well, look at your disgusting"],[325,450,"juvie rags."],[450,500,"You're telling me"],[500,592,"the daughter of an heiress"],[592,796,"can't even afford a decent outfit?"],[796,884,"And the girlfriend"],[884,1055,"of a second string quarterback"],[1055,1167,"can't even come up"],[1167,1313,"with a better comeback."],[1401,1472,"Hey, I played two and a"],[1472,1605,"half games last season."],[1605,1718,"I'm on my way to first string."],[1718,1893,"Oh, really?"],[1893,2193,"Well, then catch this."],[2531,2869,"Oh my God."],[2961,3119,"Oh my God."],[4033,4212,"For the dry cleaning bill."],[4250,4508,"There's more where that came from."],[4508,4608,"Hey it's okay."],[4608,4884,"It's okay. It's not that bad."],[5559,5613,"Baby, babe please."],[5613,5680,"I swear I didn't-"],[5680,5847,"Get the fuck out of here."],[6664,6744,"What are you doing"],[6744,6865,"sticking your dirty little nose"],[6865,7165,"in the Lancaster heiress' locker?"],[7173,7298,"This is my locker."],[7298,7374,"Open it then."],[7374,7440,"Only the real"],[7440,7524,"Lancaster heiress would"],[7524,7607,"know the combination."],[8391,8483,"Wait."],[8483,8637,"Are you?"],[8637,8712,"Oh, please."],[8712,8837,"She's a reform school rat."],[8837,8942,"Obviously, she knows"],[8942,9054,"how to pick a lock."],[9054,9138,"That's probably why"],[9138,9250,"she has all that money."],[9250,9401,"She's a thief!"],[9667,9884,"Is that the Lancaster Crest?"]],"10":[[513,667,"I didn't steal anything."],[834,946,"Everyone must gather"],[946,1034,"for an assembly"],[1034,1088,"to welcome"],[1088,1272,"our esteemed new students,"],[1272,1368,"the Lancaster heiress"],[1368,1572,"and Grayson West,"],[1572,1622,"our new"],[1622,1722,"star quarterback."],[1722,1847,"Grayson?"],[1847,2010,"The guy I met this morning."],[2010,2106,"Oh, my God, I heard"],[2106,2248,"Grayson is so hot."],[2248,2356,"He's the best football player"],[2356,2552,"in the entire country."],[2552,2715,"Back off, bitches."],[2715,2902,"He's mine."],[2902,3086,"I thought"],[3086,3303,"Jake was yours."],[3303,3374,"Oh, please."],[3374,3566,"He's just a backup option."],[3566,3653,"Don't worry."],[3653,3774,"You can have my sloppy seconds"],[3774,3945,"when I'm done with him."],[3945,4091,"Soon I'm going to be the girlfriend"],[4091,4208,"of the star football player"],[4208,4508,"and besties with the heiress."],[4708,4817,"Let's go, girls."],[5230,5530,"We'll see about that."],[6410,6539,"All right."],[6539,6669,"I'd now like to invite"],[6669,6748,"to the stage"],[6748,6936,"the head of the heiress'"],[6936,7094,"welcoming committee,"],[7161,7332,"Fallon Blakely."],[7749,8003,"Thank you, Principal Gordon."],[8003,8141,"The heriess and I are"],[8141,8270,"basically besties,"],[8270,8441,"and she wanted me to tell all that"],[8441,8537,"she is beyond"],[8537,8650,"thrilled to join us"],[8650,8812,"here at Hawthorn Prep,"],[8812,8892,"especially with"],[8892,9000,"homecoming around the corner."],[9000,9188,"Now, I'm not going to tell you"],[9188,9338,"who she plans to vote for,"],[9338,9446,"but let's just say"],[9551,9726,"she's got great taste."],[9726,9830,"Besties?"],[9830,9939,"As if I'd ever"],[9939,10172,"vote for a liar and a bully."],[10172,10285,"I need to expose"],[10285,10556,"her for the fraud she is."],[10556,10719,"Now, the heiress also asked me"],[10719,10865,"to give her a personal tour"],[10865,10973,"when she arrives."],[10973,11048,"So we're going"],[11048,11144,"to begin with-"],[11144,11273,"Where's she been?"],[11353,11469,"Excuse me?"],[11469,11561,"The heiress? You said"],[11561,11711,"you're her bestie?"],[11711,11874,"She's been missing for 12 years."],[11874,11